page.title: 09Slyne-With-Hest:Housing
page.content: Slyne-With-Hest is a residential area. Many of the houses have been built recently.The old houses are near the main road and near Hatlex Lane and the canal.Many of the houses in Slyne-With- Hest are of a modern design.The different kinds of houses vary from: semi detached,detached,terrace and bungalows.The roofs on the houses are mainly modern roofing tiles.Houses in Slyne-With-Hest are all of a different design.Gardens vary with the type of house.Most houses have garages or a car port.Extentions in Slyne-With-Hest are fairly common because of growing families.The price of houses in Slyne- With-Hest is very high compared to other local areas.There are not many cottages in Slyne-With-Hest,but modern bungalows are common.
